reviews.review_text: awesome this was the last time I saw jerry alive and I noticed he didn't look right but his playing and leads were the best by far that  I've ever seen, his jammin' was incredible ,even after all these years that has passed I still miss him,hearing this show brings me right back.if it wasn't for jerry Garcia I wouldn't be the guitar player I am today.
Best Aud source I like the sound on this best.   Cutler's live mixes in spring 95 were much better than spring 94.  The show is great.  Jerry not sounding '95' like, at all on this one.
Don't overlook '95 This is a solid AUD, sometimes sounds a bit muddy or unclear but at times you could mistake it for an FM broadcast. Cool set list, and Jerry sounds better than you might expect.
